s MP govt. will have to pay an additional Rs. 528 crore which is now paid by the central govt. under Ayushman Bharat Yojana.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bhopal/mp-to-roll-out-maha-ayushman-with-a-greater-coverage/articleshow/70032320.cms  at  "}